Siqi, wait for me.

95
00:06:11,510 --> 00:06:12,720
Wait for me.

96
00:06:15,110 --> 00:06:15,950
Why did you agree

97
00:06:15,950 --> 00:06:17,390
to stay and work for him?

98
00:06:18,550 --> 00:06:19,670
