101
00:06:24,830 --> 00:06:25,760
so I might as well work for him.

102
00:06:26,230 --> 00:06:27,200
Besides,

103
00:06:27,200 --> 00:06:28,880
maybe if we're lucky,

104
00:06:29,270 --> 00:06:30,350
