Let me see.

187
00:10:53,790 --> 00:10:54,670
Qiao Bin,

188
00:10:55,640 --> 00:10:58,030
I'll take you to the beach tomorrow.

189
00:11:04,840 --> 00:11:06,000
Loris

190
00:11:06,000 --> 00:11:08,030
