job requirements.

228
00:12:22,640 --> 00:12:23,710
Don't worry about it.

229
00:12:23,840 --> 00:12:25,520
I'll protect myself.

230
00:12:25,880 --> 00:12:26,590
Let's do this, then.

231
00:12:26,790 --> 00:12:29,350
